      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey can u help me put together a quick itinerary for my trip to tokyo next week? i'll be based around shibuya but have several meetings in marunouchi. i need to make sure i account for transit times between the two areas so i'm not late, and i also need suggestions for some quiet cafes where i can actually get some work done between sessions. thanks.",
